longBusinessSummary: Karuturi Global Limited does not have any significant operations. Previously, it was engaged in the production, selling, and export of cut roses. The company was formerly known as Karuturi Networks Limited and changed its name to Karuturi Global Limited in May 2008. Karuturi Global Limited was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Bengaluru, India.
